Achievements.Name: Welcome to Planet 51
Achievements.Description: Complete the tutorials.

Achievements.Name: The Suburbs
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Suburbs missions.

Achievements.Name: Town
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Town missions.

Achievements.Name: Desert
Achievements.Description: Complete all the Desert missions.

Achievements.Name: I've Got Antennas!
Achievements.Description: Complete all the game missions, including all tasks.

Achievements.Name: Breaking News!
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Glipforg News Paperboy".

Achievements.Name: Lawnmower Master
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Lawnmower Boy".

Achievements.Name: Glipforg Deliveries
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Glipforg Deliveries".

Achievements.Name: The Dog Catcher
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Too Many Dogs in this Town".

Achievements.Name: Born to Park
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Parking Boy".

Achievements.Name: Glipforg Taxi Driver
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "Taxi!".

Achievements.Name: Circus Cleaner
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the task "World´s cleanest circus".

Achievements.Name: Car Crusher
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in the tasks "Car Crusher", "Battle in the Stadium" and "Desert Battle".

Achievements.Name: The Fastest Driver
Achievements.Description: Complete level 10 in all race tasks.

Achievements.Name: Car Collector
Achievements.Description: Unlock all vehicles (excluding vehicles unlocked at the police station).

Achievements.Name: Sticker Collector
Achievements.Description: Collect all the stickers that you'll earn in the tasks.

Achievements.Name: Comic Fan
Achievements.Description: Find all the comic frames scattered around Planet 51.

Achievements.Name: Curious Boy
Achievements.Description: Enter every open house and building in the game.

Achievements.Name: Pro Cyclist
Achievements.Description: Travel 12 miles by bicycle.

Achievements.Name: Pro Driver
Achievements.Description: Travel 300 miles by car.

Achievements.Name: Flying Car
Achievements.Description: Perform a jump of 150 ft or more.

Achievements.Name: Careful Driver
Achievements.Description: Drive a car for 3 minutes without collisions.

Achievements.Name: Billboard Breaker
Achievements.Description: Jump through all the billboards in the game.

Achievements.Name: Slippery
Achievements.Description: Escape 40 times from your enemies by hiding in the trash cans.

Achievements.Name: Reckless Driver
Achievements.Description: Destroy 30 pieces of property in 60 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Fugitive
Achievements.Description: Elude the law enforcers 3 times in a row in the same vehicle outside of a mission.

Achievements.Name: Alien!
Achievements.Description: Achieve and maintain the maximum level of alert for 3 minutes outside of a mission.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Gardener
Achievements.Description: Complete "Neera's Garden" without cutting any flowers, touching the mole, or getting hit by water.

Achievements.Name: The Coolest Paperboy
Achievements.Description: Get "perfect" throws for all newspapers in "The Paperboy" mission.

Achievements.Name: Careful Fighter
Achievements.Description: Complete any car crusher mission without taking any damage.

Achievements.Name: Experienced Delivery Boy
Achievements.Description: Don't lose any boxes in the "A Job of Little Importance" mission.

Achievements.Name: Careful Parking Boy
Achievements.Description: Complete the "Parking Valet" mission without damaging any cars.

Achievements.Name: Sweet Cleaner
Achievements.Description: Complete the "Cleaning The Circus" mission without making King Klong angry.

Achievements.Name: Skilled Driver
Achievements.Description: Complete the "King Klong" mission without damaging the pickup.

Achievements.Name: Fast Rock Gatherer
Achievements.Description: Pick up all the special rocks in the mission "Singing in the Rocks" before any go down the drain.

Achievements.Name: Too Good to Compete
Achievements.Description: Keep first place in any racing mission for more than 1 minuteâ€¦and win!

Achievements.Name: Perfect Timing
Achievements.Description: Finish any of Chuck's missions on foot without failing any obstacle nor taking any damage from traps
